HTVdev,provides,resources,to,develop,ideas,and,applications,within,HTC,devices,It,also,enables,connection,with,HTC,and,other,developers,The,Stereoscopic,D,API,implements,stereoscopy,technology,on,the,EVO,D,to,create,glasses,free,D,imagery,The,screen,resolution,is,halved,by,blocking,the,stereo,pair,of,images,from,the,opposite,eye,s,field,of,vision,This,accommodates,both,left,and,right,images,in,the,display